WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.275 --> 00:00:02.944
The improved responsiveness and flexibility

2
00:00:02.944 --> 00:00:04.851
that comes from improved planning

3
00:00:04.851 --> 00:00:07.503
can regulate delivery lead times.

4
00:00:07.503 --> 00:00:10.435
For instance, a particular item is delivered

5
00:00:10.435 --> 00:00:13.363
within five days every time it is ordered.

6
00:00:13.363 --> 00:00:15.704
Improved responsiveness and flexibility

7
00:00:15.704 --> 00:00:17.562
may also allow an organization

8
00:00:17.562 --> 00:00:19.492
to decrease delivery lead times

9
00:00:19.492 --> 00:00:23.003
by shipping items from locations closer to the customer.

